info.description:
Buyer API Collection

- Internal (GET Buyer Application by id, Flush Cache)
    
- US (POST Buyer Application with different decisions)
- UK (POST Buyer Application with different decisions)
- CA (POST Buyer Application with different decisions)
- AU (POST Buyer Application with different decisions)

- get buyer by id v1
- get bueyr by id V2 (antichut)

item.name: UK - Buyer Application With Owner Info
UK - OApp Events for PENDING - CCJ
UK - OApp Events for PENDING - Commercial Score
UK - OApp Events for PENDING - Business Status
UK - OApp Events for PENDING - Commercial Inquiries
UK - OApp Events for DECLINE - Commercial Score
UK - OApp Events for DECLINE - Commercial Bankruptcy

item.description:
To test Approval :

- submit the app without owner info in the form folder
- Post application event payload in approved folder
    

To test Pending :

- submit the app without owner info in the form folder
- Post application event payload in pending folder
    

To test Decline :

- submit the app without owner info in the form folder
- Post application event payload in decline folder
    

To test Duplicate Fail :

- submit the app with owner info in the form folder
- Post application event payload in duplicate fail folder

item.description:
To test Approval :

- submit the app without owner info in the form folder
- Post application event payload in approved folder
    

To test Pending :

- submit the app without owner info in the form folder
- Post application event payload in pending folder
    

To test Decline :

- submit the app without owner info in the form folder
- Post application event payload in decline folder
    

To test Duplicate Fail :

- submit the app with owner info in the form folder
- Post application event payload in duplicate fail folder

item.description:
US testing is diffrent as it depends more in mock service instead of external post datqa

to test decision startegy for US please consider the mock service senarios for US

- senarios based on business and owner state
    

All mock service senarios can be found in the sheet based on the state

[https://trevipay.sharepoint.com/:x:/s/SMBTeam-SMBDev/EYGmwvnO3zZDujaU8gxY7qABFx9IeeaTzo3esQOEzFSysg?e=9AZZRJ&nav=MTVfezU5Nzg5OTBELTdGNzYtMjU0Qi05RjE4LUVCQjJDRjU2QzM5Rn0](https://trevipay.sharepoint.com/:x:/s/SMBTeam-SMBDev/EYGmwvnO3zZDujaU8gxY7qABFx9IeeaTzo3esQOEzFSysg?e=9AZZRJ&nav=MTVfezU5Nzg5OTBELTdGNzYtMjU0Qi05RjE4LUVCQjJDRjU2QzM5Rn0)

To test Approval :

- submit the app with owner info in the form folder
- Post application event payload in approved folder
    

To test Pending :

- submit the app with owner info in the form folder
- Post application event payload in pending folder
- to test pending based on diffrent senarios score,..etc please change the app state info based on mock service sheet attached above
    

To test Decline :

- submit the app in decline folder
- Post application event payload in decline folder
    

To test Duplicate Fail :

- submit the app with owner info in the form folder
- Post application event payload in duplicate fail folder
